            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steven_biko_205078",
        "quote": "Merely by describing yourself as black you have started on a road towards emancipation, you have committed yourself to fight against all forces that seek to use your blackness as a stamp that marks you out as a subservient being.",
