                "url": "/topics/committed"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steven_biko_777374",
        "quote": "Tradition has it that whenever a group of people has tasted the lovely fruits of wealth, security, and prestige, it begins to find it more comfortable to believe in the obvious lie and accept that it alone is entitled to privilege.",
